    "description": "Play with well-known historical characters from different eras and countries, such as Leonardo da Vinci, Albert Einstein, and many others! There's a common enemy traveling through time and causing mayhem. They need to gather strength in this game with simple and fun visuals but challenging mechanics, can you defeat the threat? This platformer has a lot of unusual obstacles and bosses for you to overcome and achieve victory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJump, dash and climb to overcome the challenges, each character has a unique ability for a more varied gameplay and as you progress, new concepts will emerge. In the boss levels, attack and dodge with your dash until you finally defeat him, if you're not satisfied, defeat him again in the insane mode for the most experienced only. Some scenes may contain some secrets, so pay close attention.",
